// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM is read from the DEVELOPMENT_TEAM environment
// variable at build time. Export it in your shell before running
// `flutter build ios`, or set it via Xcode → Signing & Capabilities.
// Find your 10-char Apple team ID at developer.apple.com/account.
// See the repo root README → "Set your Apple signing team".
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = $(DEVELOPMENT_TEAM)
CODE_SIGN_STYLE = Automatic
